{"word":"ἀναβλέπω","slug":"ἀναβλέπω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναβλέπω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to look up</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἀν. πρός τινα</el> <i>to look</i> him <i>in the face</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to look up at</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; also <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> cogn., <el>ἀν. φλόγα</el> <i>to cast up</i> a glance of fire, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to recover one's sight</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; <el>πάλιν ἀν.</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b> <p/></div>"}]}